uk.ac.ebi.pride.tools.dta_parser

Class DtaFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.tools.dta_parser.DtaFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JMzReader

    public class DtaFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements JMzReader
    This class represents a DTA file. Normally, a dta file can hold only one spectrum per file. There are tools that concatenate several dta files and seperate the single spectra with one or more empty line. This type of dta files is supported by this class.
    Author:
    jg
